  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a Xfce4 Appfinder</title>

    <para>
      <application>Xfce4 Appfinder</application> is a tool to find and launch
installed applications by searching the .desktop files installed on your
system.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

